msgid "The function `%s` calls itself, this creates an infinite loop"
msgstr "function `%s` ហៅខ្លួន វាផ្ទាល់ នេះបង្កើតឱ្យមាន loop មិនចេះចប់"

#: ui/UIPractice.gd:306
msgid ""
"You have a while loop that runs forever (while true) without a break "
