msgstr "ទាក់ទង មកយើង"

#: ui/screens/end_screen/SponsorlessEndScreen.tscn:204
msgid "Congratulations!"
msgstr "អបអរសាទរ!"

#: ui/screens/end_screen/SponsorlessEndScreen.tscn:211
msgid ""
"You completed Learn GDScript From Zero. You now have the basics you need "
"to make games with the Godot game engine."
msgstr ""
"អ្នកបានបញ្ចប់ Learn GDScript From Zero ហើយ។ ឥឡូវនេះអ្នកមានមូលដ្ឋានគ្រឹះដែលអ្នកត្រូវការ ដើ"
"ម្បីបង្កើតហ្គេមជាមួយ Godot game engine។"

msgid ""
"You can keep learning with the free series "
"[url=https://docs.godotengine.org/en/stable/getting_started/step_by_step/index.html]Getting"
" Started with Godot[/url]."
msgstr ""
"អ្នកអាច បន្តរៀនជាមួយ ស៊េរីឥតគិតថ្លៃ [url=https://docs.godotengine.org/en/stable/"
"getting_started/step_by_step/index.html]Getting Started with Godot[/url]។"

#: ui/screens/end_screen/SponsorlessEndScreen.tscn:224
msgid "This is an Open-Source project!"
msgstr "នេះគឺជាគម្រោង Open-Source!"

#: ui/screens/end_screen/SponsorlessEndScreen.tscn:231
msgid "Like Godot, this app and course is free and open-source."
msgstr "ដូចជា Godot ដែរ app និង វគ្គសិក្សានេះ គឺឥតគិតថ្លៃ និង open-source។"

msgid ""
"You can find the app's source code and contribute translations here: "
"[url=https://github.com/GDQuest/learn-gdscript]Learn GDScript From Zero "
"(Github repository)[/url]."
msgstr ""
